headline: Building Future-ready Skills: Girl Rising Launches RISE Educator Training in Chhattisgarh, India
summary: In partnership with Samarpit Centre for Poverty Alleviation and Social Research and HP, Girl Rising conducted a two-day teacher training workshop for their flagship RISE program on July 8th and 9th. Designed to build adolescents' confidence, agency, and future-ready skills, RISE blends social-emotional learning and digital literacy, especially in communities facing deep educational and gender inequities.
